"Practice]"
msgstr ""
"xref:{lang}/tech-practices:ROOT:aim-and-scope.adoc[Código de prácticas "
"tecnológicas]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/introduction.adoc:13
msgid ""
"xref:{lang}/tech-sovereignty:ROOT:introduction.adoc[Guide to Technological "
"Sovereignty]"
msgstr ""
"xref:{lang}/tech-sovereignty:ROOT:introduction.adoc[Guía sobre soberanía "
"tecnológica]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/introduction.adoc:14
msgid ""
"xref:{lang}/ict-procurement:ROOT:context.adoc[Guide to Public ICT "
"Procurement]"
msgstr ""
"xref:{lang}/ict-procurement:ROOT:context.adoc[Guía de compra pública de TIC]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/introduction.adoc:17
msgid ""
"This Guide spells out these principles and guidelines in a series of "
"measures and recommendations to help staff of the Municipal Institute of "
"Information Technology (IMI), the ICT body of the Barcelona City Council, in "
"their daily work on projects based on free software.  It covers aspects such "
"as:"
msgstr ""
"El presente documento concreta estos principios y directrices en un conjunto "
"de medidas y recomendaciones que deben guiar al personal del Instituto "
"Municipal de Informática (IMI) en la gestión diaria de proyectos basados en "
"software libre, en aspectos como los siguientes:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/introduction.adoc:19
msgid "Looking for and designing solutions"
msgstr "La búsqueda y diseño de soluciones"

#. type: Plain text
